comments: Davis (LAL) establishes himself in a screening position in Dort's (OKC) path and makes marginal contact as they disengage.
Replay review of the foul called on Dort (OKC) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed successful.
Favors (OKC) makes marginal contact to Westbrook's (LAL) arm as he releases his pass attempt at the end of his drive.
Giddey (OKC) cleanly dislodges the ball from Davis (LAL) during the driving shot attempt.
Westbrook (OKC) extends his hands into Bazley's (OKC) back and the contact affects his ability to retrieve the loose ball.

As Westbrook (OKC) is attempting to secure the loose ball, Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) cleanly dislodges it. Westbrook then regathers the ball and takes a controlled dribble. There is no clear and conclusive angle to determine whether or not Westbrook pins the ball against his body after the first controlled dribble. If he does not pin the ball, he continuously dribbles throughout his spin move and is legal.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) makes hand on ball contact after Westbrook (OKC) gathers the loose ball and dislodges the ball before incidental contact occurs.
Bazley (OKC) makes marginal contact with Westbrook's (LAL) body after the release of his shot near the rim.

Davis (LAL) places his hand momentarily on Favors? (OKC) hip before
immediately removing his hand.

Favors (OKC) is already in Davis' (LAL) path and is firming up when
contact occurs.
Bazemore (OKC) maintains legal guarding position defending Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) driving shot attempt.
Bazemore (OKC) makes marginal contact with Davis (LAL) as they pursue the loose ball.
Giddey (OKC) moves laterally in Monk's (LAL) path during his drive and marginal contact occurs.
Bazley (OKC) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Favors (OKC) makes marginal contact with Monk's (LAL) arm after his release on the driving shot attempt.
Favors (OKC) establishes himself in a screening position in Monk's (LAL) path and marginal contact occurs as they disengage.
Monk (LAL) brushes Favors' (OKC) shoulder as he gathers and marginal contact occurs during his shot attempt at the basket.
Anthony (LAL) is already in Dort's (OKC) path and momentarily places his hand to Dort's arm prior to disengaging.
Bazemore (LAL) places his arm to Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) front during his drive and marginal contact occurs.
Davis (LAL) is already in Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
An 8-second violation is correctly whistled against OKC.
Monk (LAL) commits a take foul on Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC).
Bazemore (LAL) and Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) engage and disengage with one another off ball.
Westbrook (LAL) commits a take foul on Dort (OKC).
All Technical Fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
